independent.description: Vehicles with model year greater than 2020 and less than 2023
Vehicles with electric range greater than 200 miles and less than 300 miles
Vehicles with electric range between 100 and 150 miles (inclusive)
Vehicles with electric range less than 50 miles
Vehicles eligible for Clean Alternative Fuel Vehicle incentives
independent.criteria: CAFV Eligibility = Clean Alternative Fuel Vehicle Eligible

independent.description: Vehicles not eligible due to low battery range
independent.criteria: CAFV Eligibility = Not eligible due to low battery range

grouped.description: Recent Tesla BEV vehicles with high range
grouped.criteria: Model Year >= 2020 AND Make = TESLA AND Electric Range > 250

grouped.description: Older PHEV vehicles from King County
grouped.criteria: Model Year < 2018 AND Electric Vehicle Type = PHEV AND County = King

grouped.description: Mid-range BEV vehicles from 2019-2021 eligible for CAFV incentives
grouped.criteria: Model Year >= 2019 AND Model Year <= 2021 AND Electric Vehicle Type = BEV AND CAFV Eligibility = Eligible
